dct_title_s: New "half-inch" cycling road maps of England & Wales : reduced by permission from the new Ordnance Survey
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Wooded areas shown pictorially. Originally issued folded in cover 19 x 11 cm.
